TOPICS COVERED (NUMPY FOR AI & MACHINE LEARNING)
Introduction to NumPy

The training session began with an introduction to NumPy (Numerical Python), one of the most important libraries used in Artificial Intelligence, Machine Learning, Data Science, and Scientific Computing. Learned that NumPy provides powerful tools for performing fast mathematical and numerical operations on large datasets. The trainer explained that almost every Machine Learning library, such as Scikit-learn, TensorFlow, and PyTorch, is built on top of NumPy.

Discussed the advantages of NumPy over Python lists, including faster execution, lower memory consumption, efficient numerical computation, and support for multidimensional arrays.

Installing and Importing NumPy

Learned how to install the NumPy library using pip and how to import it into Python programs.

Practiced importing the library using:

